data.meta_description: Jun 4, 2017 - Tsar Ivan IV The Terrible Vasilyevich Rurik (25 Aug 1530-28 Mar 1584) 1st ruler to be crowned as Tsar of All the Russians at age 16.& his 8 wives-Anastasia Romanovna, Maria Temryukovna, Marfa Sobakina, Anna Koltovskaya, Anna Vasilchikova, Vasilisa Melentyeva, Maria Dolgorukaya, Maria Nagaya.
